### JourneySense API - Mẫu gọi nhanh (dùng với REST Client / Thunder Client)
### Đổi {{baseUrl}} thành URL thực tế, ví dụ: https://localhost:7001

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001
@token = 
@registerToken = 
@paymentLinkId = 
@microExperienceId = 
@categoryId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

###############################################################################
# AUTH
###############################################################################

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "traveler@example.com",
  "password": "YourPassword123!"
}

### Gửi OTP đăng ký
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register/send-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com"
}

### Gửi lại OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register/resend-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com"
}

### Xác thực OTP (trả về registerToken)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "otp": "123456"
}

### Đặt mật khẩu (sau khi verify OTP - dùng registerToken trong header)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register/set-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{registerToken}}

{
  "password": "YourNewPassword123!",
  "confirmPassword": "YourNewPassword123!"
}

###############################################################################
# PAYMENT
###############################################################################

### Tạo link thanh toán
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Payment/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "totalAmount": 100000,
  "description": "Thanh toán gói trải nghiệm",
  "returnUrl": "https://yourapp.com/success",
  "cancelUrl": "https://yourapp.com/cancel",
  "buyerName": "Nguyễn Văn A",
  "buyerEmail": "buyer@example.com",
  "buyerPhone": "0901234567",
  "items": [
    {
      "name": "Gói trải nghiệm 1 ngày",
      "quantity": 1,
      "price": 100000,
      "unit": "gói"
    }
  ]
}

### Lấy thông tin link thanh toán
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Payment/link/{{paymentLinkId}}

### Hủy link thanh toán
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Payment/link/{{paymentLinkId}}/cancel?reason=Khách hủy

###############################################################################
# JOURNEYS
###############################################################################

### Thiết lập hành trình (vehicleType: 0=Walking, 1=Bicycle, 2=Motorbike, 3=Car)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/journeys/setup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "originAddress": "1 Công xã Paris, Bến Nghé, Quận 1, TP.HCM",
  "destinationAddress": "Bưu điện Trung tâm Sài Gòn, Quận 1, TP.HCM",
  "vehicleType": 3,
  "timeBudgetMinutes": 60,
  "maxDetourDistanceMeters": 2000
}

###############################################################################
# EXPERIENCES (cần đăng nhập)
###############################################################################

### Gửi đánh giá ghé thăm (dùng token đăng nhập)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/experiences/visit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "experienceId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "journeyId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "ratingValue": 5,
  "feedbackText": "Trải nghiệm tuyệt vời.",
  "photoUrls": ["https://example.com/photo1.jpg"]
}

###############################################################################
# MICRO-EXPERIENCES
###############################################################################

### Danh sách (query: keyword, categoryId, status)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/micro-experiences
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/micro-experiences?keyword=cafe
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/micro-experiences?categoryId={{categoryId}}&status=0

### Chi tiết theo ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/micro-experiences/{{microExperienceId}}

### Tạo mới
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/micro-experiences
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cà phê View Sài Gòn",
  "categoryId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "address": "123 Nguyễn Huệ, Quận 1, TP.HCM",
  "city": "Hồ Chí Minh",
  "country": "Việt Nam"
}

### Cập nhật (status: 0=ActiveUnverified, 1=Verified, 2=Featured, 3=NeedsUpdate, 4=Inactive, 5=Rejected)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/micro-experiences/{{microExperienceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cà phê View Sài Gòn (Đã cập nhật)",
  "categoryId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "address": "123 Nguyễn Huệ, Quận 1, TP.HCM",
  "status": 1
}

### Xóa
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/micro-experiences/{{microExperienceId}}
